WEBVTT

00:07.174 --> 00:09.510
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "WEEDS"...</i>

00:09.543 --> 00:13.046
Kimmi: [ Laughing ] WHAT?
I JUST LOVE COLLEGE
SO MUCH.

00:13.080 --> 00:14.548
ARE YOU SURE
THAT'S A GOOD IDEA?

00:14.581 --> 00:16.517
GEEZ, GOD!
DAMN IT!

00:16.550 --> 00:18.485
EVERYONE'S GONNA BE LOOKING
FOR US HERE.

00:18.519 --> 00:19.586
GOODBYE, SEATTLE.

00:19.620 --> 00:21.388
KIMMI...
YEAH?

00:21.421 --> 00:23.190
CAN I BORROW YOUR CAR?
Nancy:
YOU GOT A CAR!

00:23.223 --> 00:25.225
YOU ARE THE HERO
OF THIS FAMILY!

00:25.259 --> 00:26.860
WHAT THE FUCK
ARE YOU DOING HERE?

00:26.894 --> 00:27.794
[ MUFFLED GRUNTING ]

00:27.828 --> 00:29.963
MOM...
THE FUCKERS GOT ME.

00:29.997 --> 00:31.398
COME ON. I'VE HAD NOTHING
TO EAT IN THREE DAYS

00:31.431 --> 00:33.600
EXCEPT
FOR A LINTY‐CAR FRENCH FRY.

00:33.634 --> 00:34.635
WHERE'S MY SON?

00:39.573 --> 00:40.741
GIVE ME YOUR KEYS.

00:40.774 --> 00:42.509
I KNOW WHERE HE IS.

00:43.777 --> 00:44.878
YOU'RE NOT GONNA SHOOT ME.

00:44.912 --> 00:47.881
I WILL IF I HAVE TO.
BUT YOU DON'T HAVE TO.

00:47.915 --> 00:49.683
YOU GONNA PUT A BULLET
IN ME, MIJO?

00:49.716 --> 00:51.418
[ GUN COCKS ]
WHAT DO YOU THINK?

00:51.451 --> 00:53.720
FEMALE VOICE:
Please record your message.

00:53.754 --> 00:56.223
Nancy:
ESTEBAN, I'M A MOTHER LION.

00:56.256 --> 01:00.594
AND YOU CAN'T DEFEAT A MOTHER
LION WHEN YOU THREATEN HER CUBS.

01:00.627 --> 01:02.863
I HAVE TO DISAPPEAR NOW.

01:02.896 --> 01:06.967
GOOD LUCK WITH YOUR CRIME.

01:21.782 --> 01:23.884
Woman:
DID YOU KILL PILAR?

01:23.917 --> 01:24.918
NO.

01:24.952 --> 01:26.854
Man:
DO YOU KNOW WHO DID?

01:26.887 --> 01:27.888
NO.

01:27.921 --> 01:30.257
PILAR ZUAZO
TURNS UP DEAD.

01:30.290 --> 01:31.925
YOUR BOSS'S WIFE
GOES MISSING.

01:31.959 --> 01:35.195
ANY IDEA
WHERE SHE MIGHT BE?

01:43.871 --> 01:45.005
SAY IT.

01:45.038 --> 01:46.907
SEATTLE WAS A BUST.

01:46.940 --> 01:48.375
YOU GONNA LISTEN
TO ME NOW?

01:48.408 --> 01:49.710
YES.
WHY?

01:49.743 --> 01:51.278
YOU'RE THE GURU
OF OFF‐THE‐GRID.

01:51.311 --> 01:53.013
I'M THE GURU
OF OFF‐THE‐GRID.

01:53.046 --> 01:56.583
YOU'VE GOT ME RIGHT HERE
IN THIS CAR WITH YOU,
YOU LUCKY WOMAN, YOU,

01:56.617 --> 01:57.551
SO YOU GONNA USE ME?

01:57.584 --> 02:00.320
YOU GONNA ACCEPT MY WISDOM
AND EXPERIENCE?

02:00.354 --> 02:01.588
YOU GONNA LET ME
TAKE THE LEAD?

02:01.622 --> 02:02.623
ANDY ‐‐
RANDY.

02:02.656 --> 02:04.191
<i>RANDY...</i>

02:04.224 --> 02:08.095
I CEDE THE REINS TO YOU,
THE EXPERT, THE GURU,

02:08.128 --> 02:10.664
THE ONE WHO WILL LEAD US
IN A SAFER,

02:10.697 --> 02:12.733
MORE UNTRACKABLE
DIRECTION.

02:12.766 --> 02:15.536
THANK YOU!
IT'S A GREAT HONOR.

02:15.569 --> 02:17.437
IT'S AN HONOR
THAT I DON'T TAKE LIGHTLY ‐‐

02:17.471 --> 02:18.739
TO PROTECT, TO GUIDE ‐‐

02:18.772 --> 02:19.940
JUST FUCKING LAY IT OUT!

02:19.973 --> 02:21.742
FINE, FINE.
HERE WE GO.

02:21.775 --> 02:24.545
TO QUOTE BILL MAHER,
"NEW RULES."

02:24.578 --> 02:26.980
NUMBER ONE ‐‐
KEEP MOVING.

02:27.014 --> 02:30.484
WE NEED TO WIDEN THE GAP
BETWEEN US AND OUR AGGRESSORS.

02:30.517 --> 02:33.086
THAT MEANS AT LEAST ANOTHER
24 HOURS ON THE ROAD,

02:33.120 --> 02:38.625
NO STOPPING, NO EXCEPTIONS
EXCEPT FOR GAS AND POTTY.

02:38.659 --> 02:40.360
HARDCORE.

02:40.394 --> 02:43.664
RULE NUMBER TWO ‐‐
THIS ONE IS KEY ‐‐

02:43.697 --> 02:45.399
NO SOCIAL INTERACTIONS.

02:45.432 --> 02:49.136
WE GO WAY UNDERGROUND,
SEAL OURSELVES OFF.

02:49.169 --> 02:52.472
I'M TALKING bin LADEN,
THE UNABOMBER,

02:52.506 --> 02:56.043
THAT GUY SLY
FROM SLY AND THE FAMILY STONE.

02:56.076 --> 02:57.578
WHO?
EXACTLY.

02:57.611 --> 02:59.213
NANCE,
HOW'S THIS SOUNDING?

02:59.246 --> 03:01.782
GREAT. MOVEMENT.
ISOLATION. MM‐HMM.

03:01.815 --> 03:03.817
OKAY. ANYONE HAVE
ANY QUESTIONS SO FAR?

03:03.851 --> 03:06.220
YEAH. DO I GET
A ROAD‐TRIP SPIRIT NAME?

03:06.253 --> 03:08.155
NO ONE'S CHASING YOU.
ARE YOU KIDDING?

03:08.188 --> 03:10.424
I OWE DANA THOUSANDS
IN CHILD SUPPORT.

03:10.457 --> 03:11.525
HOW ABOUT "TED"?

03:11.558 --> 03:14.761
OR "COWARD WHO LED A CAR
OF MEXICANS TO SEATTLE."

03:14.795 --> 03:16.597
EH, "TED" WORKS.

03:16.630 --> 03:18.365
SILAS,
YOU OKAY BACK THERE?

03:18.398 --> 03:20.100
YEAH. I'M GREAT.

03:20.133 --> 03:21.602
WE'LL STOP SOON.
AH!

03:21.635 --> 03:24.671
JUST FOR LUNCH!
I PROMISE.

03:24.705 --> 03:26.740
THAT'S IT.
THEN BACK ON THE ROAD.

03:26.773 --> 03:29.576
OFF‐THE‐GRID.
BILL MAHER.

03:35.115 --> 03:37.084
WE SHOULD TAKE
THE LEWIS AND CLARK TRAIL.

03:37.117 --> 03:39.753
IT GOES FROM WASHINGTON STATE
TO WASHINGTON, D. C.

03:39.786 --> 03:41.054
Silas: WHY DO YOU KNOW
THESE THINGS?

03:41.088 --> 03:42.155
I'M AN AUTODIDACT.

03:42.189 --> 03:43.724
ALSO, THERE'S A BROCHURE
UP FRONT.

03:43.757 --> 03:45.959
NO HISTORIC TRAILS.

03:45.993 --> 03:48.228
WE GOT TO THINK
MORE UNPREDICTABLY.

03:48.262 --> 03:50.397
NOW, WHEN I TREKKED
ACROSS ALASKA,

03:50.430 --> 03:52.499
WE ONLY TOOK
EVEN‐NUMBERED HIGHWAYS

03:52.533 --> 03:54.434
AND AVOIDED
ALL SUSPENSION BRIDGES.

03:54.468 --> 03:56.403
THAT BABY
DOESN'T LOOK MEXICAN.

03:56.436 --> 03:58.438
YEAH, HE'S HALF, BUT MOM DOESN'T
LIKE US MENTIONING IT.

03:58.472 --> 04:00.707
WELL, WHEN SHE COMES BACK
FROM THE BATHROOM,

04:00.741 --> 04:03.043
SHE CAN COMPLAIN ABOUT IT.

04:07.514 --> 04:10.350
♪♪ WELL, I'M A SNAGGLE‐TOOTH
MAMA, DON'T KNOW NO SHOES ♪♪

04:10.384 --> 04:12.519
♪♪ I GOT A TIN‐ROOF TAN ♪♪

04:12.553 --> 04:15.656
♪♪ WITH MY CORNBREAD DADDY
RIGHT BY MY SIDE ♪♪

04:15.689 --> 04:18.192
♪♪ WE DO THE BEST THAT WE CAN ♪♪

04:18.225 --> 04:20.928
♪♪ I LIVE SO FAR OUT
DOWN THE COUNTRY ROAD ♪♪

04:20.961 --> 04:23.163
♪♪ THERE AIN'T NOTHIN'
FOR HOURS ♪♪

04:23.197 --> 04:26.166
♪♪ BY THE TIME I GET BACK
FROM THE GROCERY STORE ♪♪

04:26.200 --> 04:28.235
